recipesJson.name: Fruity pebbles cheesecake
recipesJson.author: Tootall
recipesJson.description: Just an easy good  twist on a standard cereal flavor. This is a good shake and vape. I was inspired by the juice that the guy from ambitions vapor on you tube is always vaping. And  i have obviously been on a cheesecake roll I have made a lot of cheesecakes lately lol.

reviews.text: Kind of hits the profile. I get mostly fruit loops though.
